WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:08.943
Good morning, everybody. Thank you for joining us again today. We're going to pray, of course, like we always do.

00:00:08.944 --> 00:00:14.781
I want to go over some of the things the Lord showed us yesterday in prayer, and I feel the urgency of the hour.

00:00:14.782 --> 00:00:20.319
First off, I want to say thank you all for joining me, but we have a lot of work to do.

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:24.159
We're going to pray for the nation and for President Trump and his safety.

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:32.252
We'll pray for all the things the Lord has shown us, and we'll just go over some of the things that the Lord showed us yesterday.

00:00:32.253 --> 00:00:41.359
But yesterday, just the pulse of everything, I've never seen it like this before.

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:49.038
And that's why I thought it was really cool because whenever the Lord was showing me in the spirit, I saw a wall, a watchman's wall.

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:57.439
I was on the wall, and it was a beautiful stone wall. It wasn't like bricks; it was like rock.

00:00:57.440 --> 00:01:04.376
And I was on this rock, and I was looking and there were portals that looked like wormholes.

00:01:04.377 --> 00:01:16.689
The only way I can describe it to you is like yellow, bright light portals, but there were one, two, three, four, and they went down the line.

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:23.455
And the Lord said, "You can pick and choose. Every one of these right now is vital to pray over.

00:01:23.456 --> 00:01:36.788
I have much to show you because of what's happening with the urgency of the hour."If you don't know, I think you'd have to have your wood completely wet to not realize that Jesus is coming.

00:01:36.789 --> 00:01:40.099
He's coming. That's what I'm trying to tell y'all. He is coming. Jesus is coming.

00:01:40.100 --> 00:01:43.599
And your wood would have to be completely wet for you not to see it.

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:51.919
That's what I'm trying to say. Did I butcher that? I probably did, didn't I? But I'm trying to tell you that it's time to wake up.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:02:02.718
And so I saw the wall, and every single one of the portals that were up on this wall was an urgency in the spirit realm to pray over.

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:09.118
And he said, "You can pick and choose today which one you want to go down."And he's never given me that option before.

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:13.439
So I was kind of scattered because I was like, "Well, which one is vital to you?

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:19.619
Which one do you want?"Every one of these is a necessity for where we are right now.

00:02:19.620 --> 00:02:42.134
This is very—and I could see, and this is cool as it was panning before my eyes, I could see pictures like you would see on a real-life reel on YouTube. It was panning before my eyes.

00:02:42.135 --> 00:03:00.559
The screen looked like a live movie, and in every single one of them, I could see terrorist attacks, the finances of the nation, President Trump's health, so many different things going down, and every single one of them is vital.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:06.799
After I walked up to the wall, I just went, "Well, I'll just scattershot this thing.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:37.518
We'll pray into all of them."So we prayed for a long time, and I said, "I'm not leaving until I feel like I at least hit almost every single one of these, even if it's just for a couple of minutes."I didn't know how to really handle it because I've never been given that option.

00:03:37.519 --> 00:03:46.958
So as I was looking into this and I jumped into the portal, I could see the river of it and he said, "Flow in this."So I was praying.

00:03:46.959 --> 00:03:53.839
Then I started praying for the drones and 911 distractions.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:04:01.338
I could see a plot from the enemy, and the Lord said, "This is not a terrorist attack.

00:04:01.339 --> 00:04:10.318
This is an act of war from what has infiltrated America."They are sleeper cells that are truly hidden.

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:28.936
They're sleeping, and you're not going to hear internet chatter of some ISIS enthusiast going, "Hey, we're going to do this and that."The Lord was showing me, he said, "These are trained soldiers. There's no chatter.

00:04:28.937 --> 00:04:55.758
What you are hearing is that secret signal that is like a Morse code that is only broadcast at certain times of day, once a week or once a month."It was coming from a signal and it sounded like the little thing you push the button on the Speak & Spell.

00:04:55.759 --> 00:05:08.478
Do you remember Speak & Spell in the '80s? It sounded like a voice, like Speak & Spell. And I could hear the numbers and it was a deciphered code.

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:18.239
It was the deciphered code that was coming to the soldiers, the enemy within, the Red Dawn experience that I keep telling y'all about all the time.

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:23.530
I say we got to pray against the Red Dawn experience. We got to pray against the enemy within.

00:05:23.531 --> 00:05:27.758
This is an infiltration of the enemy that is not terrorists.

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:33.359
I would say, like I said, it's an act of war. These are trained soldiers and they look like Special Ops.

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:38.319
But I was praying into this and I heard the Speak & Spell sound. It was a voice.

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:59.670
But as they would get the code, it would only last for a couple of seconds, but they knew when to get the code of when they were to be commissioned to do it, like "stand down"or "go ahead."It was a code and they would have to write down the numbers and then they would decipher it with the deciphering sheet.

00:05:59.671 --> 00:06:07.279
So I saw it was very well thought out. And the Lord said they're not using the internet.

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:12.559
They're using a different means, like Cold War old communications.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:28.239
So I saw it. So they were listening for their code. Then I saw drones and the Lord was showing me 911 distractions.

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:36.673
I saw that they would try in the days ahead to create an event to make all the police go over there.

00:06:36.674 --> 00:06:58.257
You make a little event happen over here so they think it's a major event, and all the law enforcement would flood to this area because they think, "Oh, this is the big thing."But the big thing was down the road.

00:06:58.258 --> 00:07:11.918
So I saw a planned thing to disrupt 911 services to distract from the main event.

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:18.638
I saw a hospital in Boston. I saw a Red Cross. I saw a Red Cross on this.

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:23.714
It looked like something on the medical ship for the Navy. It was a big Red Cross.

00:07:23.715 --> 00:07:30.099
I don't know if this is type and shadow metaphor or whatever, but because sometimes it is when the Lord's showing me stuff.

00:07:30.100 --> 00:07:37.229
It's not always just black and white. It's like the seven fat cows and seven skinny cows.

00:07:37.230 --> 00:07:51.767
When you're looking at it, it doesn't mean anything about the cows; it means famine's coming and seven years of blessing and seven years of famine.

00:07:51.768 --> 00:08:07.119
So I see the building and the Lord said, "Look at the hospital."But I could see snipers on the top of certain buildings trying to take out law enforcement when they came, hiding on top of buildings in black outfits.

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:11.359
And they were trying to not just get police officers, but firefighters.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:17.011
And the Lord said, "Pray for the firefighters. Pray for your law enforcement. Pray for the FBI.

00:08:17.012 --> 00:08:41.918
Pray for Homeland Security."That's why I was praying over all your law enforcement. Pray over New Orleans, Nashville, and Boston.

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:52.239
They were in a line: Boston, Nashville, and New Orleans—the furthest south, mid, and north. I thought it was interesting.

00:08:52.240 --> 00:09:13.066
But the way He had me praying over three cities—Minneapolis; Omaha, Nebraska; and these cities where they have cells of these people in them—I was praying over that.

00:09:13.067 --> 00:09:24.586
Then I was shown the Boston Red Sox and the New York Yankees. I don't know why; I saw the stadiums and was praying over these two rivals.

00:09:24.587 --> 00:09:30.746
Pray over the games; pray over baseball in the days ahead. Just pray over baseball, America's pastime.

00:09:30.747 --> 00:09:38.728
They always call it America's pastime, right? I still love baseball; baseball is amazing to me.

00:09:38.729 --> 00:09:49.779
I love the playoffs; it's my thing. But praying over our baseball games, over Judge.

00:09:49.780 --> 00:09:57.199
I saw Judge's face in the Yankees. I saw him and I don't know why, but I knew it was the Yankees.

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:07.039
Then praying over the World Cup with the Mexican team, Mexico, with the green and white jerseys, praying over this.

00:10:07.040 --> 00:10:20.308
I saw them; I saw the World Cup. I saw the drones. The drones had a bubble around them.

00:10:20.309 --> 00:10:31.428
It was an electric bubble that looked like one of those balls you touch at a science fair where the electricity touches your finger.

00:10:31.429 --> 00:10:44.799
It had a force field around it. The drones had a thin membrane that looked like a force field with electricity beams going all around it.

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:56.329
And as you would use a jammer to knock it down—I saw our law enforcement had jammers that look like little guns, like little razor things—but they couldn't.

00:10:56.330 --> 00:11:08.239
They had a mathematical equation. It was a mathematical code that you had to penetrate with something like a virus.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:14.159
Excuse my ignorance, but this is all I know how to do to describe to you what I was seeing in the spirit.

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:29.599
They needed a virus to break the code; they needed something to break the cipher of the bubble that protects the drone. I saw all these drones had big wings, four of them.

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:51.439
They had a payload, a white box underneath the drone, and the Lord said, 'This is a payload.'So I saw that and I saw the drones being used, but they have come out with a frequency to jam the jammers so that they don't take them down.

00:11:51.440 --> 00:12:01.278
It was, like I said, a mathematical code. I don't know what I'm saying; I'm just telling you what I saw.

00:12:01.279 --> 00:12:09.610
I'm telling it to you, Brandon. This is all like rocket science to me. I'm just trying to tell you what the Lord was showing me.

00:12:09.611 --> 00:12:14.359
I thought it was very interesting because I saw the bubble around these things.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:30.239
They were trying to plan a swarm, like bees, to all come out. It's too much—what do you do with a swarm?

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:42.078
It was very dark. As I was looking into New Orleans, I heard 'Bay of Pigs'again.

00:12:42.079 --> 00:12:50.798
I saw the fox in the Bay of Pigs area look towards New Orleans. The Lord said, 'Pray over New Orleans.

00:12:50.799 --> 00:12:58.287
Pray over this.'So, I'm seeing in part; we'll see if God gives us any more today.

00:12:58.288 --> 00:13:02.958
It isn't about us. We attract to deflect. We keep our eyes on Jesus.

00:13:02.959 --> 00:13:14.139
It's so important that we decrease and He increase, that no matter how much we see or what God shows us, we keep the main thing the main thing, and it's Him.

00:13:14.140 --> 00:13:20.879
It's all about Him, and it will continue to be about Him. It's not about Brandon Biggs, my wife, or my son.

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:29.548
It's always about giving God glory for using us in these last days because He could use any one of you. It's to keep humble.

00:13:29.549 --> 00:13:38.159
He rebuked me even; sometimes people want to talk to you, and I go, 'Lord, why do they want to bother me?'I think I'm just a real private person; I kind of stay to myself.

00:13:38.160 --> 00:13:50.799
He said, 'Brandon, what makes you think they want to talk to you?'I said, 'Well, they're the ones talking to me.'He said, 'It's Christ in you.

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:58.479
They see Jesus; they see Me in you, Son. They're pulling from the anointing.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:02.078
It's not you they're after; they want the glory; they want the anointing.

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:07.359
They sense something, and that's why they're coming.'But it's not you.

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:12.839
Anytime you start thinking it's you—'Why do they want to talk to me?'—well, they don't want to talk to you.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:23.492
What makes you think they do? I repented immediately. He said, 'There goes a root that can turn into a root of pride real quick.

00:14:23.493 --> 00:14:42.212
Let it die.'I said, 'Yes, Lord.'It's always staying on that line, staying in that balance of where He's at, staying on the life source, that you are always decreasing.

00:14:42.213 --> 00:14:47.634
You attract to deflect. You attract to deflect even in your thoughts.

00:14:47.635 --> 00:14:54.879
'Why do they want to talk to me? Why do they want to bother me?'They don't. They're after the anointing. They need a touch from Jesus.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:58.479
Every single one of them, even if they see a mirror, they see Jesus in you.

00:14:58.480 --> 00:15:08.878
Because in the days ahead—this is where I'm going with this—there'll be a lot of you that are going to be the catchers.

00:15:08.879 --> 00:15:15.838
The pitcher is going to throw it hot; you're going to get a fastball.

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:27.019
When they're coming into the body of Christ—these sinners, the unsaved, the people who need to get Jesus—they're coming in hot.

00:15:27.020 --> 00:15:31.278
I'm trying to describe how I saw it in the vision. The Lord said, 'You're catching.

00:15:31.279 --> 00:15:40.159
Are you ready? Do you have your mitts ready? Are you ready to receive the people that are coming?'Be patient with my babies.

00:15:40.160 --> 00:15:49.999
There will be many of you that walk with the glory on you. There'll be many of you that walk with the presence of God, with healings and signs and wonders in these last days.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:16:00.479
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few. Always attract to deflect.

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:10.905
Give Him glory for everything you're about to see. It's all about Jesus all the time.

00:16:10.906 --> 00:16:14.114
It's so important. I listen to Kathryn Kuhlman all the time.

00:16:14.115 --> 00:16:28.495
I thought, 'Man, this lady is really dramatic,'but when you feel that you've grieved the Holy Spirit—like I did last night with some thoughts I had—the Lord corrects me.

00:16:28.496 --> 00:16:36.879
I walk a very thin line; to whom much is given, much is required.

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:48.638
I always check my thermostat. Where are you with your walk with the Lord today?

00:16:48.639 --> 00:16:57.919
Have you checked your spiritual thermostat today? Where were you when you woke up? I had to go back and look at all the mercy scriptures.

00:16:57.920 --> 00:17:11.759
I look at all the times I think, 'Well, God's mad at me; He's upset.'And He said, 'Brandon, go look at all my mercy scriptures. Go meditate on mercy today.

00:17:11.760 --> 00:17:40.798
How much do I love you?'I said, 'Yeah, His goodness and His mercy.'Even when you get off track and He checks your heart, you think, 'Oh, I don't want to mess up.

00:17:40.799 --> 00:18:01.263
I want to keep right with You.'But He shows me He has mercy. God loves you. I don't even know why I'm crying. It hit me hard.

00:18:01.264 --> 00:18:11.999
I told Diana, 'We have to go drive around for a little bit,'because that's where I worship, in my car, and I drive and pray over the city.

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:22.558
In the middle of the night, I said, 'Let's go. I want to drive and pray.'I'm going over all the things that He's talking to me about regarding the end times.

00:18:22.559 --> 00:18:35.119
And I always keep my thermostat hot. I try really hard, but even whenever he tells me, "Read these scriptures about mercy today."What are you going through?

00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:43.279
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're going through and meditate on them. And today I needed mercy.

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:52.319
Today I said, "God, you know, I feel like you're irritated at me or whatever."And you know, correction comes.

00:18:52.320 --> 00:18:55.439
Correction is not always fun when he corrects you. It's a spanking.

00:18:55.440 --> 00:19:03.519
And at the same time, you go, "Are we cool? Can we fist bump? Are we all right?"And of course we're right.

00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:07.918
But he said, "Oh, Brandon, meditate on my mercy towards you.

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:14.558
Meditate on my love towards you today. Get rid of the stinking thinking.

00:19:14.559 --> 00:19:23.279
I'm not mad at you. I have longsuffering. I love you. I love your wife. I love your kids.

00:19:23.280 --> 00:19:31.519
I correct those I love."And correction makes the bridle of the horse's mouth go.

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:37.599
And the more you're broken, the less he has to jerk on that bridle to get you to move.

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:46.558
If you have to yank a horse, that horse is in rebellion; a horse just has to be led. And the more you just barely do that, the horse will move.

00:19:46.559 --> 00:19:52.887
It doesn't have to take a hard pull unless the horse is not doing what you tell it to do.

00:19:52.888 --> 00:20:04.639
But you just barely lead that horse and that horse will just go and run. It doesn't take much. And that's when you're pliable.

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:09.519
God will do the exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:24.749
If you're pliable in your life and keeping him the main thing, keeping my eyes on him, you have to yield yourself to him every day.

00:20:24.750 --> 00:20:38.519
I just thought it was interesting some of the things that I'm going through and just how he's teaching me and standing against the things that have been trying to come against me in the spirit realm and learning the authority of the believer.

00:20:38.520 --> 00:20:48.479
You can hear Sister Billye Brim talk about the authority of the believer, Pastor Candace, but you can parrot it really easy.

00:20:48.480 --> 00:21:00.079
You can be a parrot and just quote Sister Billye's book, "The Authority of the Believer,"and Brother Hagin, and you can read that and go, "Yeah, I've got the authority of the believer.

00:21:00.080 --> 00:21:06.079
Of course I do. Yeah, that's right, pastor. High five."And you can be all excited about it.

00:21:06.080 --> 00:21:20.679
But when the enemy comes and the roaring lion comes at your house and you're sitting there and they're not there, the book is a couple feet away and you know the enemy is there and he's knocking at your door.

00:21:20.680 --> 00:21:46.255
I heard an audible voice saying, "I'm mad about yesterday and what we did yesterday."I stopped and I started praying in the spirit and the Lord said, "Stand against this."I get the word down and I quote it out of my mouth, but I don't want to parrot something that I've heard from somebody else.

00:21:46.256 --> 00:21:56.409
I want it to be a Rhema to me. And the only way you're going to get Rhema is by you meditating on the word. You're going to have to get Ephesians down in your heart.

00:21:56.410 --> 00:22:15.159
You're going to have to get the Bible and you read it and you meditate on it and you apply it and you get the supplements like "The Authority of the Believer"and you read that and you apply it. At the entrance of his word brings forth light.

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:29.639
And the more you get that word down inside your heart, the more you get it coming through your eyes, it will renew your mind and then you'll realize, "This isn't me parroting a word and a book anymore.

00:22:29.640 --> 00:22:39.919
This is becoming a Rhema word to my spirit and it has power and authority."When a word becomes Rhema to you, power and authority will come out of you.

00:22:39.920 --> 00:22:48.019
So the more you meditate on the word, the more you get it down inside your heart, you're not just parroting what your pastor's saying.

00:22:48.020 --> 00:22:53.496
I really want to encourage you. It starts with parroting. It's like babies.

00:22:53.497 --> 00:23:01.199
They imitate their mom and daddies. Be imitators of God as dear children imitate their fathers.

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:10.273
So imitate the Lord. But the only way you're going to do that is by watching and looking at him by mirroring that.

00:23:10.274 --> 00:23:18.878
This is God speaking to me. The word is alive and it is written for you to get that down inside of you.

00:23:18.879 --> 00:23:33.519
If you want to know who God is, read this Bible. When you get that word inside of you, it will change you from the inside out. The entrance of his word brings forth light.

00:23:33.520 --> 00:23:42.026
So I'm trying to help you because there's so many new believers that come on here and a lot of people that don't know anything about the word and they want to know, "Why am I still bound?

00:23:42.027 --> 00:23:49.625
Why am I broke? Why am I not making it financially? How come I'm not making it with my health?

00:23:49.626 --> 00:23:59.109
My marriage is a wreck and I'm strung out on drugs; I can't get free from that."You will know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:23:59.110 --> 00:24:05.359
I have so many people say, "I need to have demons cast out of me."Yeah, you might.

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:14.136
But the only way you're going to remain free, even if you got them cast out of you, is getting this word of God inside of you. Or he's going to bring eight more of his friends with him.

00:24:14.137 --> 00:24:22.079
They're going to bring a bunch of his little buddies and they're going to say, "Hey, we can go in there,"because he doesn't have the word inside of him still.

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:35.359
The only way that you're going to stay free is getting a foundation of the word of God inside of you.

00:24:35.360 --> 00:24:44.450
You can quote scripture, but until it is real to you, it's like saying "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star."You can quote things out of your mouth and parrot things.

00:24:44.451 --> 00:24:56.079
But the enemy knows when you know. When you submit yourself therefore unto God, you resist the devil and he will flee.

00:24:56.080 --> 00:25:04.039
He knows when you know. He's seeking whom he may devour. Who can he devour?

00:25:04.040 --> 00:25:08.239
The one that doesn't have the word inside of their heart and is rooted and grounded in love.

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:13.679
Faith works by love. So you've got to walk in love. You've got to check your love thermostat.

00:25:13.680 --> 00:25:18.639
So if your faith doesn't feel like it's working, check your love walk.

00:25:18.640 --> 00:25:31.269
How do you treat the people around you? Are you treating them cranky? Are you rude or hateful?

00:25:31.270 --> 00:25:40.239
God is love and the word of God will flow out of you when you get rooted in love.

00:25:40.240 --> 00:25:53.678
Love has to be priority because faith works by love. I don't understand why I'm not having any breakthrough?

00:25:53.679 --> 00:26:01.489
Check your love walk. Check how you treat people. Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:26:01.490 --> 00:26:12.498
Love is not fretful. Love is not resentful. 1 Corinthians 13, I believe it is.

00:26:12.499 --> 00:26:23.239
Read it. Get love down inside of you. Love never fails. I'm trying to tell you all this because of what I've seen coming.

00:26:23.240 --> 00:26:27.038
And you're going to have to know this. You're going to have to understand Psalm 91.

00:26:27.039 --> 00:26:34.879
You're going to have to understand Psalm 23. You're going to have to get it rooted in your heart.

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:42.252
I try very hard not to preach fear. War is not going to happen on our soil, Brandon.

00:26:42.253 --> 00:26:47.865
These things aren't going to happen with us. I pray that all the time.

00:26:47.866 --> 00:26:55.918
But I'm going to tell you, for the things I've seen in visions and the storms that I've seen coming, I've seen great shakings coming to America.

00:26:55.919 --> 00:27:01.599
America as you know it is going to change majorly in the days ahead.

00:27:01.600 --> 00:27:05.404
The Lord said, "I've given you a window with President Trump.

00:27:05.405 --> 00:27:11.092
What will you do with the window? Will you squander it or will you use it?

00:27:11.093 --> 00:27:15.038
I've given you a window of opportunity here, a four-year window.

00:27:15.039 --> 00:27:22.959
Now we're down to two and a half years."And that's if we can get him on the other side by praying.

00:27:22.960 --> 00:27:27.999
It's not just automatic. We have to pray for his health, his marriage, and his children.

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:31.839
We have to pray for the attacks that are coming against his life.

